title: Windows 10 Enterprise 2015 LTSB x64 (MULTi-18) May 2016 {Gen2}
description:
* Windows 10 Enterprise 2015 LTSB x64 (MULTi-18) May 2016 


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* This release contains one ISO [SOURCE ISO] and 17 executable svf-files.
* All exe-files are created from original MSDN releases. 

* This is done with SmartVersion, a program that calculates the
* difference between two files (one of which is used as the source)
* and then creates an svf-file based on that difference.

[ DOWNLOAD INFO ]

* Download the Source ISO and preferred language
* If you want en-US then just download the SOURCE ISO

* Run the exe-file in the same folder as the SOURCE ISO.
* This will extract the ORIGINAL ISO in the selected language.
* Hashes & sources attached in a separate .txt

[ CONTENTS ]

* Integrated:

* Servicing Stack Update(s):
* KB3141032
* CumulativeUpdate(s):
* KB3156387
* Security Update (Flash Player for IE):
* KB3157993
* OOBE Update (July 23, 2015):
* KB3074686
* OOBE update (November 18, 2015):
* KB3116097
* OOBE updates (December 8, 2015):
* KB3118714 and KB3119598
* OOBE update (December 15, 2015):
* KB3122962
* Dynamic Update (for updating Installation Media):
* KB3106937
* .NET Framework 4.6.2:
* KB3120830

* Setupcomplete / Post-install:

* Enable .NET Framework 3.5
* KB890830
* Windows Defender Updates

[ LANGUAGES ]

* ar-SA = Arabic
* da-DK = Danish
* de-DE = German
* el-GR = Greek 
* en-GB = English (GB)
* en-US = English (US)
* es-ES = Spanish
* fi-FI = Finnish 
* fr-FR = French 
* it-IT = Italian
* nb-NO = Norwegian 
* nl-NL = Dutch
* pl-PL = Polish 
* pt-BR = Brazilian 
* pt-PT = Portuguese
* ru-RU = Russian
* sv-SE = Swedish
* tr-TR = Turkish

[ FEATURES ]

* UEFI-ready 
* (Use attached Rufus USB-tool to make UEFI-bootable).
* Diagnostics and Recovery Toolset 10.0 (Microsoft DaRT)

* Windows 10 Enterprise 2015 LTSB
* Windows 10 Enterprise 2015 LTSB - KMS

* KMS = Activation by KMS
 (Exclusions made in Defender)
